<BIBL><HI>K. Richard II.</HI></BIBL></Q>
<P><HI>The following pa&s;&s;age from</HI> Otway <HI>&s;hould gradually warm into</HI> Rapture.</P>
<Q><L>Can there in woman be &s;uch glorious faith!</L>
