<BIBL><HI>Theodo&s;ius.</HI></BIBL></Q>
<P>Humility <HI>and</HI> In&s;inuation <HI>are thus happily &s;et forth by</HI> Shake&s;peare.</P>
<Q><L>Thus, Brutus, did my ma&s;ter did me kneel;</L>
<L>Thus did Marc Antony bid me fall down,</L>
