<BIBL><HI>Julius Cae&s;ar.</HI></BIBL></Q>
<P>Di&s;&s;imulation, <HI>which requires the &s;ame tone of ex|pre&s;&s;ion, we find in the&s;e lines of</HI> Young.</P>
<Q><L>It hurts not me, my lord, but as I love you:</L>
